    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主线画出来：Pending收到付款后变成Confirmed，Confirmed开始履约进入Processing，Processing发货后变成Shipped，最后送达Delivered结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
